{"code":200,"status":"OK","data":{"number":153,"ayahs":[{"number":3215,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3215.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/3215.mp3"],"text":"۞ فَمَا كَانَ جَوَابَ قَوْمِهِۦٓ إِلَّآ أَن قَالُوٓا۟ أَخْرِجُوٓا۟ ءَالَ لُوطٍۢ مِّن قَرْيَتِكُمْ ۖ إِنَّهُمْ أُنَاسٌۭ يَتَطَهَّرُونَ","numberInSurah":56,"juz":20,"manzil":5,"page":382,"ruku":330,"hizbQuarter":153,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":27,"name":"سُورَةُ النَّمۡلِ","englishName":"An-Naml","englishNameTranslation":"The Ant","revelationType":"Meccan"}},{"number":3216,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3216.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/3216.mp3"],"text":"فَأَنجَيْنَٰهُ وَأَهْلَهُۥٓ إِلَّا ٱمْرَأَتَهُۥ قَدَّرْنَٰهَا مِنَ ٱلْغَٰبِرِينَ","numberInSurah":57,"juz":20,"manzil":5,"page":382,"ruku":330,"hizbQuarter":153,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":27,"name":"سُورَةُ النَّمۡلِ","englishName":"An-Naml","englishNameTranslation":"The Ant","revelationType":"Meccan"}},{"number":3217,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3217.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/3217.mp3"],"text":"وَأَمْطَرْنَا عَلَيْهِم مَّطَرًۭا ۖ فَسَآءَ مَطَرُ ٱلْمُنذَرِينَ","numberInSurah":58,"juz":20,"manzil":5,"page":382,"ruku":330,"hizbQuarter":153,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":27,"name":"سُورَةُ النَّمۡلِ","englishName":"An-Naml","englishNameTranslation":"The Ant","revelationType":"Meccan"}},{"number":3218,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3218.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/3218.mp3"],"text":"قُلِ ٱلْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ وَسَلَٰمٌ عَلَىٰ عِبَادِهِ ٱلَّذِينَ ٱصْطَفَىٰٓ ۗ ءَآللَّهُ خَيْرٌ أَمَّا يُشْرِكُونَ","numberInSurah":59,"juz":20,"manzil":5,"page":382,"ruku":331,"hizbQuarter":153,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":27,"name":"سُورَةُ النَّمۡلِ","englishName":"An-Naml","englishNameTranslation":"The Ant","revelationType":"Meccan"}},{"number":3219,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3219.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/3219.mp3"],"text":"أَمَّنْ خَلَقَ ٱلسَّمَٰوَٰتِ وَٱلْأَرْضَ وَأَنزَلَ لَكُم مِّنَ ٱلسَّمَآءِ مَآءًۭ فَأَنۢبَتْنَا بِهِۦ حَدَآئِقَ ذَاتَ بَهْجَةٍۢ مَّا كَانَ لَكُمْ أَن تُنۢبِتُوا۟ شَجَرَهَآ ۗ أَءِلَٰهٌۭ مَّعَ ٱللَّهِ ۚ بَلْ هُمْ قَوْمٌۭ يَعْدِلُونَ","numberInSurah":60,"juz":20,"manzil":5,"page":382,"ruku":331,"hizbQuarter":153,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":27,"name":"سُورَةُ النَّمۡلِ","englishName":"An-Naml","englishNameTranslation":"The Ant","revelationType":"Meccan"}},{"number":3220,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3220.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/3220.mp3"],"text":"أَمَّن جَعَلَ ٱلْأَرْضَ قَرَارًۭا وَجَعَلَ خِلَٰلَهَآ أَنْهَٰرًۭا وَجَعَلَ لَهَا رَوَٰسِىَ وَجَعَلَ بَيْنَ ٱلْبَحْرَيْنِ حَاجِزًا ۗ أَءِلَٰهٌۭ مَّعَ ٱللَّهِ ۚ بَلْ أَكْثَرُهُمْ لَا يَعْلَمُونَ","numberInSurah":61,"juz":20,"manzil":5,"page":382,"ruku":331,"hizbQuarter":153,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":27,"name":"سُورَةُ النَّمۡلِ","englishName":"An-Naml","englishNameTranslation":"The Ant","revelationType":"Meccan"}},{"number":3221,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3221.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/3221.mp3"],"text":"أَمَّن يُجِيبُ ٱلْمُضْطَرَّ إِذَا دَعَاهُ وَيَكْشِفُ ٱلسُّوٓءَ وَيَجْعَلُكُمْ خُلَفَآءَ ٱلْأَرْضِ ۗ أَءِلَٰهٌۭ مَّعَ ٱللَّهِ ۚ قَلِيلًۭا مَّا تَذَكَّرُونَ","numberInSurah":62,"juz":20,"manzil":5,"page":382,"ruku":331,"hizbQuarter":153,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":27,"name":"سُورَةُ النَّمۡلِ","englishName":"An-Naml","englishNameTranslation":"The Ant","revelationType":"Meccan"}},{"number":3222,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3222.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/3222.mp3"],"text":"أَمَّن يَهْدِيكُمْ فِى ظُلُمَٰتِ ٱلْبَرِّ وَٱلْبَحْرِ وَمَن يُرْسِلُ ٱلرِّيَٰحَ بُشْرًۢا بَيْنَ يَدَىْ رَحْمَتِهِۦٓ ۗ أَءِلَٰهٌۭ مَّعَ ٱللَّهِ ۚ تَعَٰلَى ٱللَّهُ عَمَّا يُشْرِكُونَ","numberInSurah":63,"juz":20,"manzil":5,"page":382,"ruku":331,"hizbQuarter":153,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":27,"name":"سُورَةُ النَّمۡلِ","englishName":"An-Naml","englishNameTranslation":"The Ant","revelationType":"Meccan"}},{"number":3223,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3223.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/3223.mp3"],"text":"أَمَّن يَبْدَؤُا۟ ٱلْخَلْقَ ثُمَّ يُعِيدُهُۥ وَمَن يَرْزُقُكُم مِّنَ ٱلسَّمَآءِ وَٱلْأَرْضِ ۗ أَءِلَٰهٌۭ مَّعَ ٱللَّهِ ۚ قُلْ هَاتُوا۟ بُرْهَٰنَكُمْ إِن كُنتُمْ صَٰدِقِينَ","numberInSurah":64,"juz":20,"manzil":5,"page":383,"ruku":331,"hizbQuarter":153,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":27,"name":"سُورَةُ النَّمۡلِ","englishName":"An-Naml","englishNameTranslation":"The Ant","revelationType":"Meccan"}},{"number":3224,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3224.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/3224.mp3"],"text":"قُل لَّا يَعْلَمُ مَن فِى ٱلسَّمَٰوَٰتِ وَٱلْأَرْضِ ٱلْغَيْبَ إِلَّا ٱللَّهُ ۚ وَمَا يَشْعُرُونَ أَيَّانَ يُبْعَثُونَ","numberInSurah":65,"juz":20,"manzil":5,"page":383,"ruku":331,"hizbQuarter":153,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":27,"name":"سُورَةُ النَّمۡلِ","englishName":"An-Naml","englishNameTranslation":"The Ant","revelationType":"Meccan"}},{"number":3225,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3225.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/3225.mp3"],"text":"بَلِ ٱدَّٰرَكَ عِلْمُهُمْ فِى ٱلْءَاخِرَةِ ۚ بَلْ هُمْ فِى شَكٍّۢ مِّنْهَا ۖ بَلْ هُم مِّنْهَا عَمُونَ","numberInSurah":66,"juz":20,"manzil":5,"page":383,"ruku":331,"hizbQuarter":153,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":27,"name":"سُورَةُ النَّمۡلِ","englishName":"An-Naml","englishNameTranslation":"The Ant","revelationType":"Meccan"}},{"number":3226,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3226.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/3226.mp3"],"text":"وَقَالَ ٱلَّذِينَ كَفَرُوٓا۟ أَءِذَا كُنَّا تُرَٰبًۭا وَءَابَآؤُنَآ أَئِنَّا لَمُخْرَجُونَ","numberInSurah":67,"juz":20,"manzil":5,"page":383,"ruku":332,"hizbQuarter":153,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":27,"name":"سُورَةُ النَّمۡلِ","englishName":"An-Naml","englishNameTranslation":"The Ant","revelationType":"Meccan"}},{"number":3227,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3227.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/3227.mp3"],"text":"لَقَدْ وُعِدْنَا هَٰذَا نَحْنُ وَءَابَآؤُنَا مِن قَبْلُ إِنْ هَٰذَآ إِلَّآ أَسَٰطِيرُ ٱلْأَوَّلِينَ","numberInSurah":68,"juz":20,"manzil":5,"page":383,"ruku":332,"hizbQuarter":153,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":27,"name":"سُورَةُ النَّمۡلِ","englishName":"An-Naml","englishNameTranslation":"The Ant","revelationType":"Meccan"}},{"number":3228,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3228.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/3228.mp3"],"text":"قُلْ سِيرُوا۟ فِى ٱلْأَرْضِ فَٱنظُرُوا۟ كَيْفَ كَانَ عَٰقِبَةُ ٱلْمُجْرِمِينَ","numberInSurah":69,"juz":20,"manzil":5,"page":383,"ruku":332,"hizbQuarter":153,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":27,"name":"سُورَةُ النَّمۡلِ","englishName":"An-Naml","englishNameTranslation":"The Ant","revelationType":"Meccan"}},{"number":3229,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3229.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/3229.mp3"],"text":"وَلَا تَحْزَنْ عَلَيْهِمْ وَلَا تَكُن فِى ضَيْقٍۢ مِّمَّا يَمْكُرُونَ","numberInSurah":70,"juz":20,"manzil":5,"page":383,"ruku":332,"hizbQuarter":153,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":27,"name":"سُورَةُ النَّمۡلِ","englishName":"An-Naml","englishNameTranslation":"The Ant","revelationType":"Meccan"}},{"number":3230,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3230.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/3230.mp3"],"text":"وَيَقُولُونَ مَتَىٰ هَٰذَا ٱلْوَعْدُ إِن كُنتُمْ صَٰدِقِينَ","numberInSurah":71,"juz":20,"manzil":5,"page":383,"ruku":332,"hizbQuarter":153,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":27,"name":"سُورَةُ النَّمۡلِ","englishName":"An-Naml","englishNameTranslation":"The Ant","revelationType":"Meccan"}},{"number":3231,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3231.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/3231.mp3"],"text":"قُلْ عَسَىٰٓ أَن يَكُونَ رَدِفَ لَكُم بَعْضُ ٱلَّذِى تَسْتَعْجِلُونَ","numberInSurah":72,"juz":20,"manzil":5,"page":383,"ruku":332,"hizbQuarter":153,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":27,"name":"سُورَةُ النَّمۡلِ","englishName":"An-Naml","englishNameTranslation":"The Ant","revelationType":"Meccan"}},{"number":3232,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3232.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/3232.mp3"],"text":"وَإِنَّ رَبَّكَ لَذُو فَضْلٍ عَلَى ٱلنَّاسِ وَلَٰكِنَّ أَكْثَرَهُمْ لَا يَشْكُرُونَ","numberInSurah":73,"juz":20,"manzil":5,"page":383,"ruku":332,"hizbQuarter":153,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":27,"name":"سُورَةُ النَّمۡلِ","englishName":"An-Naml","englishNameTranslation":"The Ant","revelationType":"Meccan"}},{"number":3233,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3233.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/3233.mp3"],"text":"وَإِنَّ رَبَّكَ لَيَعْلَمُ مَا تُكِنُّ صُدُورُهُمْ وَمَا يُعْلِنُونَ","numberInSurah":74,"juz":20,"manzil":5,"page":383,"ruku":332,"hizbQuarter":153,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":27,"name":"سُورَةُ النَّمۡلِ","englishName":"An-Naml","englishNameTranslation":"The Ant","revelationType":"Meccan"}},{"number":3234,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3234.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/3234.mp3"],"text":"وَمَا مِنْ غَآئِبَةٍۢ فِى ٱلسَّمَآءِ وَٱلْأَرْضِ إِلَّا فِى كِتَٰبٍۢ مُّبِينٍ","numberInSurah":75,"juz":20,"manzil":5,"page":383,"ruku":332,"hizbQuarter":153,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":27,"name":"سُورَةُ النَّمۡلِ","englishName":"An-Naml","englishNameTranslation":"The Ant","revelationType":"Meccan"}},{"number":3235,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3235.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/3235.mp3"],"text":"إِنَّ هَٰذَا ٱلْقُرْءَانَ يَقُصُّ عَلَىٰ بَنِىٓ إِسْرَٰٓءِيلَ أَكْثَرَ ٱلَّذِى هُمْ فِيهِ يَخْتَلِفُونَ","numberInSurah":76,"juz":20,"manzil":5,"page":383,"ruku":332,"hizbQuarter":153,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":27,"name":"سُورَةُ النَّمۡلِ","englishName":"An-Naml","englishNameTranslation":"The Ant","revelationType":"Meccan"}},{"number":3236,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3236.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/3236.mp3"],"text":"وَإِنَّهُۥ لَهُدًۭى وَرَحْمَةٌۭ لِّلْمُؤْمِنِينَ","numberInSurah":77,"juz":20,"manzil":5,"page":384,"ruku":332,"hizbQuarter":153,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":27,"name":"سُورَةُ النَّمۡلِ","englishName":"An-Naml","englishNameTranslation":"The Ant","revelationType":"Meccan"}},{"number":3237,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3237.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/3237.mp3"],"text":"إِنَّ رَبَّكَ يَقْضِى بَيْنَهُم بِحُكْمِهِۦ ۚ وَهُوَ ٱلْعَزِيزُ ٱلْعَلِيمُ","numberInSurah":78,"juz":20,"manzil":5,"page":384,"ruku":332,"hizbQuarter":153,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":27,"name":"سُورَةُ النَّمۡلِ","englishName":"An-Naml","englishNameTranslation":"The Ant","revelationType":"Meccan"}},{"number":3238,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3238.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/3238.mp3"],"text":"فَتَوَكَّلْ عَلَى ٱللَّهِ ۖ إِنَّكَ عَلَى ٱلْحَقِّ ٱلْمُبِينِ","numberInSurah":79,"juz":20,"manzil":5,"page":384,"ruku":332,"hizbQuarter":153,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":27,"name":"سُورَةُ النَّمۡلِ","englishName":"An-Naml","englishNameTranslation":"The Ant","revelationType":"Meccan"}},{"number":3239,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3239.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/3239.mp3"],"text":"إِنَّكَ لَا تُسْمِعُ ٱلْمَوْتَىٰ وَلَا تُسْمِعُ ٱلصُّمَّ ٱلدُّعَآءَ إِذَا وَلَّوْا۟ مُدْبِرِينَ","numberInSurah":80,"juz":20,"manzil":5,"page":384,"ruku":332,"hizbQuarter":153,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":27,"name":"سُورَةُ النَّمۡلِ","englishName":"An-Naml","englishNameTranslation":"The Ant","revelationType":"Meccan"}},{"number":3240,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3240.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/3240.mp3"],"text":"وَمَآ أَنتَ بِهَٰدِى ٱلْعُمْىِ عَن ضَلَٰلَتِهِمْ ۖ إِن تُسْمِعُ إِلَّا مَن يُؤْمِنُ بِـَٔايَٰتِنَا فَهُم مُّسْلِمُونَ","numberInSurah":81,"juz":20,"manzil":5,"page":384,"ruku":332,"hizbQuarter":153,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":27,"name":"سُورَةُ النَّمۡلِ","englishName":"An-Naml","englishNameTranslation":"The Ant","revelationType":"Meccan"}}],"surahs":{"27":{"number":27,"name":"سُورَةُ النَّمۡلِ","englishName":"An-Naml","englishNameTranslation":"The Ant","revelationType":"Meccan"}},"edition":{}}}